{"word":"G5383 - φιλοπρωτεύω - philoprōteúō - fil-op-rote-yoo'-o - Love to have the preeminence","slug":"G5383","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φιλοπρωτεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>philoprōteúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>fil-op-rote-yoo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Love to have the preeminence"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C6;&#x03B9;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03C9;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - philopro&#x0304;teuo&#x0304;</b> - <i>fil-op-rot-yoo'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5384\">G5384</a> and <a href=\"#/G4413\">G4413</a>; to <i>be fond of being first</i>, that is, <i>ambitious</i> of distinction: - love to have the preeminence."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2705\">G2705</a>, <a href=\"#/G5367\">G5367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5368\">G5368</a>, <a href=\"#/G5369\">G5369</a>, <a href=\"#/G5370\">G5370</a>, <a href=\"#/G5373\">G5373</a>, <a href=\"#/G5377\">G5377</a>, <a href=\"#/G5384\">G5384</a>, <a href=\"#/G5387\">G5387</a>"}]}